Big week! We’ve now upgraded our first skills to @Rasa_HQ -based trainable intents and entities parsing with a regression tool for progressively updating training models based on user interactions. Meaning: much smarter about learning new skills and vocabularies!

More often than not NLP is a black box model hooked to one specific part of your product, and then never iterated upon. At NLP-centric startups (like @Rasa_HQ or @huggingface ) integration points for ML models have to be everywhere in the product
